description.en:
Exam is compulsory for students who do not write a MA thesis or MA project.
Arcaheology, archival studies, art history, Estonian history, contemporary history, general history:
- Research paper, 6 credits, 45 000-65 000 characters. The topic is approved by the head of the department;
- Exam based on literature, 9 credits: the list of literature will be provided by the head of department.

Teacher of history and civics:
- Research paper, 6 credits, 45 000-65 000 characters. The topic is approved by the head of department;
- Exam based on literature, 6 credits, the list of literature will be given by the head of department;
- A school class demonstration, 3 credits.
